      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are cooked, add the<strong> drained linguine</strong> to the pan with a couple of splashes of the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Squeeze in the juice of half your<strong> lemon</strong> and stir until the sauce sticks to the<strong> </strong>linguine – this is your <strong>king prawn, garlic & chilli linguine</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1599558438557-x200.jpg",
